Text:
For those who are worried, the keygen is not a virus, it's from EDGE, who usually pack their keygens with a .EXE file compressor, like most groups do. I uploaded it to virusscan.jotti.org; the result was it was packed with the Krunchy. I sent the file to Sophos who emailed me back and said it is merely a keygen for norton ghost.
